  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个GitLab SSH请求的完整链路图。用户通过SSH push代码的时候，流量会先经过LoadBalancer，然后到NGINX，最后才进到GitLab Shell。这个流程得交代清楚。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Client",
        "LoadBalancer",
        "NGINX",
        "GitLab Shell"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，那NGINX这边我注意到有个路由逻辑，是根据TCP ConfigMap来做的对吧？这个需要画成loop的形式吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "NGINX",
        "route",
        "TCP ConfigMap",
        "loop"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，NGINX内部会根据TCP ConfigMap做路由判断，这个循环得保留。然后GitLab Shell收到SSH之后，要去调Webservice的API做鉴权。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "NGINX",
        "TCP ConfigMap",
        "GitLab Shell",
        "Webservice",
        "API"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，我把NGINX到GitLab Shell的SSH连接画上了，还有GitLab Shell调Webservice的HTTP GET /API。Webservice返回401或200，这个双向箭头我也标注了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "NGINX",
        "GitLab Shell",
        "Webservice",
        "HTTP GET /API",
        "HTTP 401/200"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "鉴权通过之后，GitLab Shell还要通过gRPC去调Gitaly拿仓库数据。这里Gitaly自己也要再调一次Webservice做二次鉴权，这个容易漏掉。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "GitLab Shell",
        "Gitaly",
        "gRPC",
        "Webservice",
        "API"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下，Gitaly调Webservice也是HTTP GET /API，返回同样的401/200吗？还有gRPC的箭头方向，是双向的还是单向的？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Gitaly",
        "Webservice",
        "HTTP GET /API",
        "HTTP 401/200",
        "gRPC"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，Gitaly和Webservice之间也是同样的API调用。gRPC是双向的，GitLab Shell发请求给Gitaly，Gitaly处理完要返回结果。最后整个链路要原路返回给Client。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Gitaly",
        "Webservice",
        "gRPC",
        "GitLab Shell",
        "NGINX",
        "LoadBalancer",
        "Client"
      ],
